{"tid":464113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"空地發現「無頭男屍」　生殖器「整塊被挖走」","createTime":"2017-11-10T08:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T08:16:24.000Z","uid":70985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b6dad504b2f34f3307a284f4ab9997c8fa1ddec0","tid":464113,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2916/d2916171.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2916%2Fd2916171.jpg&h=56492eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥庫奧蒂特蘭伊斯卡伊（Cuautitl&aacute;n Izcalli）一處空地7日發現一具年輕男性的屍體，屍體的褲子被脫至膝蓋，生殖器部位整個被挖下來，頭顱也和身體分離，被丟在數公尺外。<br />\n<br />\n根據墨西哥《千禧報》報導，屍體一早7點多被附近民眾發現，穿著黑色運動上衣、藍色牛仔褲，及白色運動鞋，目擊者表示，「<span style=\"color: red;\">只有看到身體，頭顱不見了，褲子被脫了一半，下體整個不見了，那邊變成一個大凹洞</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n▼男子褲子被脫下一半，下體整組消失。<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2916/d2916169.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2916%2Fd2916169.jpg&d=mra2Gp7%2BDn3%2B5CFdgs%2Bt7J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1ed842ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2916/d2916169.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n警方到場以後指出，男子年約20左右，生殖器和周遭部分被挖了下來，頭顱則在幾公尺外被找到，「附近有一塊紙板，似乎寫著和屍體有關的訊息，但因為天氣的關係，已經看不清楚了。」當地居民透露，前幾天有一名17歲少年去參加聚會後失蹤，似乎和死者是同一人，但警方沒有證實此消息。<br />\n<br />\n此事也引起許多墨西哥網友關注，他們多不感到意外，並認為死者應是犯了罪，才遭到私刑殺害，並痛批警方的處理態度散漫，助長類似事件不斷發生，「他可能性侵了別人家的女孩，才會被對方家人報復吧！」「私刑事件一直發生，警方卻無能為力，說真的，住在墨西哥越來越沒安全感。」「一定跟女人有關係，不然沒事不會砍下體。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n▼頭顱被警方找到。<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2916/d2916168.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2916%2Fd2916168.jpg&d=mra2Gp7%2BDn3%2B5CFdgs%2Bt7J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6000f2ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2916/d2916168.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171110/1049338.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171110%2F1049338.htm&d=mra2Gp7%2BDn3%2B5CFdgs%2Bt7J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0a5feba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171110/1049338.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2780a0e385b4e8a0ab664d60878bd4b335fa939c","tid":464113,"uid":22869,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"褲子被脫了一半，下體整個不見了，那邊變成一個大凹洞<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/161312_44427b6a230049ecac860082cc98ea54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F161312_44427b6a230049ecac860082cc98ea54.jpg&h=e76de008&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18206a5416189f29ea2cced26e78919fcae94d4d","tid":464113,"uid":52511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2916/d2916171.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2916%2Fd2916171.jpg&h=56492eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥庫奧蒂特蘭伊斯卡伊（Cuautitl&aacute;n Izcalli）一處空地7日發現一具年輕男性的屍體，屍體的褲子被脫至膝蓋，生殖器部位整個被挖下來，頭顱也和身體分離，被丟在數公尺外。<br />\n<br />\n根據墨西哥《千禧報》報導，屍體一早7點多被附近民眾發現，穿著黑色運動上衣、藍色牛仔褲，及白色運動鞋，目擊者表示，「<span style=\"color: red;\">只有看到身體，頭顱不見了，褲子被脫了一半，下體整個不見了，那邊變成一個大凹洞</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n▼男子褲子被脫下一半，下體整組消失。<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2916/d2916169.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/l